      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my awesome car and it's looking for a new home! It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. I've made sure to keep up with everything, so it's ready to hit the road whenever you are. It drives like a dream and is just a great, dependable ride overall. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have\u2014come take a look!",
