    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six with VarioCam Plus, delivering linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. Recent preventative maintenance includes a dual-row IMS bearing retrofit and a new rear main seal. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings, while the factory four-piston monoblock calipers provide consistent, fade-free deceleration. A mechanically sound, driver-focused example ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
