    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s in really wonderful shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
