    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. This unit delivers exceptional power through a crisp Getrag M-DCT gearbox and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains sharp with its aluminum-intensive suspension geometry and EDC (Electronic Damping Control) intact. Notably, the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014critical maintenance items for this platform\u2014have been proactively serviced. While showing minor signs of use typical for its age, the vehicle maintains excellent structural integrity and a clean undercarriage, making it a prime candidate for the discerning driver seeking peak naturally aspirated performance.",
